Wished extensions and improvements:

- Set a default Reference collection. Some ideas:

    @Foo artist:Bar AND album:Baz
    =>
      Intersection:
        Equals ('artist', 'foo') for:
          Reference: 'Collections/Foo'
        Equals ('album', 'bar') for:
          Reference: 'Collections/Foo'

    artist:Bar@Foo AND album:Baz
    =>
      Intersection:
        Equals ('artist', 'foo') for:
          Reference: 'Collections/Foo'
        Equals ('album', 'bar') for:
          Reference: 'All Media'

    artist:Bar OR ( @Foo album:Baz AND title~"foo" ) OR title:foo*bar
    =>
      Union:
        Equals ('artist', 'Bar') for:
          Reference: 'All Media'
        Intersection:
          Equals ('album', 'Baz') for:
            Reference: 'Collections/Foo'
          Match ('title', '*foo*') for:
            Reference: 'Collections/Foo'
        Match ('title', 'foo*bar') for:
          Reference: 'All Media'


- Merge IDS sequences in one IdList:

    #1,3-5 #10 #8-12
    =>
      IdList: (1, 3, 4, 5, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12)


- "Advanced" merge:

    #1,2 OR title:foo OR #3,4
    =>
      Union:
        IdList: (1, 2, 3, 4)
        Equals ('title', 'foo') for:
          Reference: 'All Media'

    artist:foo OR ( @Foo artist:Baz OR title~foobar ) OR title:bar
    =>
      Union:
        Equals ('artist', 'foo') for:
          Reference: 'All Media'
        Equals ('artist', 'Baz') for:
          Reference: 'Collections/Foo'
        Match ('title', '*foobar*') for:
          Reference: 'Collections/Foo'
        Equals ('title', 'bar') for:
          Reference: 'All Media'

